        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for copy of <hi rend="italic">Cross and self-fertilisation</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Reports instances of cross-fertilisation in maize,</p>
            <p>and succession of forms of flowers on Isle of Wight.</p> 
<p>Asks CD’s suggestions for his second edition of Julius von Sachs’s <hi rend="italic">Text-book of botany</hi>.</p> 
